This four bedroom boasts custom trim throughout, a spacious flex room, all upgraded light fixtures, butcher block countertops, custom tile shower in master, a beautifully customized ship-lap wall, and a screened in back porch, perfect for early morning coffee. Call today to schedule your personal tour!
